  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295900/extras/15e17c4995c4c9dddf1c9dddb3dce6c4.avif?t=1743518318\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295900/extras_big/15e17c4995c4c9dddf1c9dddb3dce6c4.avif?t=1743518318 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Parkour Challenger is a platform game set in various environments. The goal is to complete each course. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 levels, each with a unique environment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable by 1 to 4 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple objective</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge saws, bullets, and lasers!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump over a tank, a knight, or even a rocket!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ability to shrink to slip through narrow passages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is no walk in the park, hurry before the lava catches up with you!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295900/extras/15e17c4995c4c9dddf1c9dddb3dce6c4.avif?t=1743518318\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295900/extras_big/15e17c4995c4c9dddf1c9dddb3dce6c4.avif?t=1743518318 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Parkour Challenger is a platform game set in various environments. The goal is to complete each course. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 levels, each with a unique environment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable by 1 to 4 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple objective</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge saws, bullets, and lasers!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump over a tank, a knight, or even a rocket!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ability to shrink to slip through narrow passages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is no walk in the park, hurry before the lava catches up with you!</p></li></ul>",
